result.title: Invitation For ACM ICPC Chennai, India Regional Replay Round on CodeChef
result.content:
Hi All,

ACM ICPC Chennai, India regional replay is running on CodeChef. You can participate in it as a team at https://www.codechef.com/CHN17ROL. Please note that it is a team contest. The contest will end at Monday 2 AM IST (around 33 hours from now).

NOTE: The contest has been extended by one day.

Happy programming,

Regards,
Praveen Dhinwa
Team CodeChef

P.S. Sorry for a late announcement :(
